User to Message: Each user can send multiple messages, but each message is sent by exactly one user. This is a "one-to-many" relationship. Each message is associated with one user.

Chat to Message: Each chat can have multiple messages, but each message belongs to exactly one chat. This is also a "one-to-many" relationship. Each message is associated with one chat.

User to Chat: Users participate in chats by sending messages. Each chat can have multiple users, and each user can participate in multiple chats. This is a "many-to-many" relationship. 